{"tid":710590,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大家喺情緒低落嘅時候會做咩？","createTime":"2018-06-21T01:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T09:39:56.000Z","uid":31979,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd85f3787f59a99a9ba205aab2f03bcd5f742ee2","tid":710590,"uid":31979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:24:17.000Z","msg":"大路行為：<br />\n<br />\n1. 打丁<br />\n2. 食零食/大擦一餐<br />\n3. 瞓覺<br />\n4. 食煙/飲酒<br />\n5. 做運動<br />\n6. 打機<br />\n7.同朋友傾訴<br />\n<br />\n喺香港做上班狗好難捱，有無巴絲有獨特嘅減壓良方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d897a1ecdd5f22029abacf19dfde87672d1fac","tid":710590,"uid":106296,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"消失於朋友圈自閉<br />\n因為我唔鍾意聽安慰說話<br />\n自己生活下 做自己鍾意既野 諗通左 忘記左 舒服返 就會出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b13c60f89168cf98cb4990127b64b4f00f473d","tid":710590,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:41:01.000Z","msg":"搵人傾，將自己心裡面嘅嘢講晒出嚟，喊得出就喊埋出嚟，舒發下自己內心，唔好鬱住自己，主動約下朋友去街，冇街去就落街做下運動，唔好留係屋企咁多，盡量令自己好忙"},{"pid":"67bc4cb41772a4bf1352fa49e4dd5fef821cd823","tid":710590,"uid":7615,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:41:20.000Z","msg":"諗下點自殺 通常諗一排就會冇咁低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13aeaa9ff98728ee99a6c8cdfc2fbfcc453ee7ed","tid":710590,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"睇綜藝節目"},{"pid":"8150b42223bc113aa6f80bf286b6a537d8243998","tid":710590,"uid":13878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:44:31.000Z","msg":"揸架車出去邊聽歌邊吹風邊食煙"},{"pid":"fa6fa5968fe9a2bd205344ccca37b848c23cfdf5","tid":710590,"uid":118186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06